name: John Garth
bio: Travel as has always been a big to me.  I love getting out of North Dakota and seeing the rest of the country.  I have visited many states, but now I am branching out to other countries.

name: Sandy Reynolds
bio: Our family of 5 loves to travel whenever we can.  Road trips, visits to relatives, or even trips overseas.  Lately, we have had a strong interest in the culture and history of England.
